snippet.title: Pathankot Terror Attack Update: Four Militants Gunned Down

localized.description:
Two Indian jawans have been martyred in an ongoing terror attack on Pathankot Air Force station in Punjab. This follows the kidnap drama of Gurdaspur SP a day before. Four of the seven terrorists have been downed in the ongoing encounter.
